Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Oobleck?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.01,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm afraid those bags won't be necessary, girls
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:08.63,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as you've opted to shadow a Huntsman on what is now essentially a reconnaissance mission
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:11.55,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I can assure you, we will not be establishing a single base of operations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:14.38,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, we will be traversing several miles of hazardous wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:17.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and making camp in any defendable locations we may stumble upon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:21.04,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I packed all of our essentials myself, plotted our air course, and readied the airship, and..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.92,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Doctor Oobleck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:25.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't earn the Ph.D. for fun, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:26.90,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhhh..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:30.84,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, children, according to my schedule, we are already three minutes behind..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:31.97,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, alright then..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:37.18,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're going to save the world with Doctor Oobleck-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.63,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay yeah when you say it out loud, it sounds worse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.45,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:45.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going on world-saving missions without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hurt, sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.19,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:49.79,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That last one's not your fault, though
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:50.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:53.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds exciting, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just outside the kingdom..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! So are we!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:00.94,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren and Nora wanted to shadow the sheriff of a nearby village
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:02.14,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We set out tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:04.04,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can party with us tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.04,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We're shadowing a crime specialist, all inner-city detective stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.55,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We get junior badges
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:15.75,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We normally go to the city with you guys, which means stuff's always exploding and junk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:20.32,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So we thought this might be a better way to check out the kingdom when it's, you know..normal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:20.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Four minutes, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:29.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:31.00,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish us luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:41.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I just never saw you as much of a fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.81,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit I fancy myself more of an..intellectual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:47.78,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can assure you, as a Huntsman, I've had my fair share of tussles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:48.81,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are truffles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:50.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sprout?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:51.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Brussels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:52.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:57.09,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Given my expertise in the field of history as well as my dabblings in the archaeological surveys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dear headmaster saw fit to assign me to this particular..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:00.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Assignment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What does history have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, what a preposterous question, you silly girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:07.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, history is the backbone of our very society!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.47,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And the liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.69,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the kidneys, if I were to wager
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And that means..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:15.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The southeast quadrant outside of Vale is home to wild forests and deep caves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:19.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it is also the location to one of the kingdom's greatest failures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.58,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain Glenn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.99,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it was an expansion of Vale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:27.11,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end it was overrun by Grimm and fenced off from the rest of the city
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:30.93,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! And now it stands abandoned as a dark reminder
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And a likely place for a hideout
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.90,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:58.87,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, you still may be students
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.81,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But as of this moment, your first mission as a Huntress has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,From this point forward, you need to do exactly as I say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.00,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:07.70,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to leave all of your bags back at school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But, uh..you hadn't told us to listen to you yet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not wrong..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.94,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Ruby, leave your bag here, we can pick it up upon our return
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:21.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But I, well..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:25.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, what in the world could you possibly have in that bag that could be so important to bring it with..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back in the bag..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:36.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to investigate an abandoned urban jungle teeming with death and hostility
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.17,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And you brought..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:38.89,D,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:40.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uhh..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.25,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:47.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Canines are historically known for their perceptive nose and heightened sense of sound
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.35,D,,0000,0000,0000,,making them excellent companions for hunts such as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a genius
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.63,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're your orders, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.26,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yes, straight to the chase, I like it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:02.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,As you've been informed, the southeast area has been marked as a recent hotspot for Grimm activity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:06.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there are several possible explanations for this behavior, one of which being..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:06.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.38,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:11.47,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,A creature of Grimm approximately one hundred yards from us at this very moment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.53,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:19.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.76,D,,0000,0000,0000,,There're a number of reasons why Grimm will congregate in this particular area
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.53,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The most likely of which will be their attraction to negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.59,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Envy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:29.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.73,D,,0000,0000,0000,,All qualities that are likely held by our hidden group harboring ill intent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So..what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.70,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We wait
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:39.63,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We track
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,If this specimen leads us to its pack, that pack may subsequently lead us to our prey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.79,D,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:49.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's uncertain, hours, days, weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, lone Grimm have been known to stay isolated from the pack for months
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.70,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's the whole pack
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:55.57,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.00,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And now they've seen us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:57.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And now they've seen us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.97,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it tracking is out of the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,An accurate assumption, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.23,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the plan, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.71,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you're capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears, Zwei~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, piece of cake
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.60,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not celebrate yet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.18,D,,0000,0000,0000,,For I am certain this is the first bout of many
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.37,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:35.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, there doesn't seem to be any signs of criminal operations in this sector
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.58,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, moving on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:44.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doc, you know, I was actually looking forward to seeing a pro Huntsman in action
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:48.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, fighting, or at least helping us fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.00,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I am in action
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.50,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Scouring the ruins of this once great city for any signs of irregularity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.55,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Not every mission is filled with daring and heroism, girls
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.85,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it's just a heightened form of extermination
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, this is a job
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.90,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And you all signed up for it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.33,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I do hope you understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.48,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.85,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Yang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose this line of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:19.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to fight monsters and save..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is what you do, I want to know why you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The honest reason as to why you want to be a Huntress
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The honest reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thrill-seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:38.07,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna travel around the world and get wrapped up in as many crazy adventures as I can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:41.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I help people along the way, then that's even better
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a win-win, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.37,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Miss Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:53.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl born into fame and fortune such as yourself certainly doesn't need the extra work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why choose this, over a cushy job in Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as you said
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.27,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Schnee, I have a legacy of honor to uphold
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I realized I was capable of fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:08.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no longer a question of what I would do with my life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my duty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you, Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to carry yourself with a sense of purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.48,D,,0000,0000,0000,,There's too much wrong in this world to just stand by and do nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.99,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Inequality, corruption, someone has to stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:39.63,D,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.46,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Uh..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.23,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, uhh..are we ready to keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I believe that will have to do for today
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.73,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be dark soon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You three, set up camp in that building
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and please do make sure that there are no more of those..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.01,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Your leader and I are going to secure the perimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:11.90,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Ruby
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.65,D,,0000,0000,0000,,WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:32.25,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? It was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That, my dear girl, is a Grimm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:42.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kill it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:48.27,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid your sniper rifle will do nothing more than agitate a Grimm of that size
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.04,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But..what if it attacks us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.11,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Fret not, Ruby, those Goliaths are not concerned with us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby, not every Grimm is mindless
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather not every Grimm is still mindless
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.71,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the Grimm you see before you are so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,so superior to the Grimm you fought
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,that they've undoubtedly lived hundreds of years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:10.58,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And in that time between killing humans and attacking our borders, they've done one important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,They've learned
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:15.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,They've learned that when they attack our borders, they're likely to die
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and what we lack in strength, we make up for in will
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.53,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and that killing one human will only bring more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.31,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.60,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they still so close to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.60,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.84,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Oobleck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.05,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:52.59,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Wondering why I've been interrogating your teammates all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.92,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you want to become a Huntsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Look around and tell me what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of old buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:06.11,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, empty streets..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I see lives that could have been saved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.87,D,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Huntsman, it is my job to protect the people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.71,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And although I'm capable of doing it with traditional weaponry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:19.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I can make a much larger impact if I do it with my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,As a teacher, I'm able to take knowledge, the most powerful weapon of them all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.74,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and place it in the hands of every student that passes through my classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at this wasteland, and I see lives that could have been saved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also see an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:37.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity to study these ruins and learn from this tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore become stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Huntsman, Ruby
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.17,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there is nothing else in this world..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.65,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.38,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we didn't find anything
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We've always been fortunate enough to be in the right place at the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't always have luck on our side
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:04.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:08.87,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, about..upholding the legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to it than that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.16,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me too, I mean..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:15.98,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, either
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I want to do, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.89,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd always take things one step at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.92,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.32,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We know why we're here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.49,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wonderful, a textbook campfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.67,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:35.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So..warm..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.33,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, eat your dinners and hurry to bed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:38.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot of ground to cover tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.60,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll need you to take turns keeping watch over our temporary abode
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.46,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Any volunteers for first watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.71,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did Oobleck ask you why you wanted to be a Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.35,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean..what did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm..no, he didn't, weird
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.44,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, good night, guys
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.93,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.37,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will be better tomorrow
